attributes.action: Ban police from using lethal methods when dogs are out of control
attributes.additional_details: We think that many dogs could have been brought under control without being killed and that this has caused a lot of distress.
attributes.background: We want the government to require police to use non-kill methods with out of control dogs. Stun not gun.
